  <description>
    <p>2Ship2Harkinian does for Majora's Mask what Ship of Harkinian did for Ocarina of Time:
      a recompiled port that brings the original game to new platforms with a variety of
      fixes and improvements. We are careful to put any and all changes to the
      game behind toggles, so that by default you get the authentic experience.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><em>Higher framerate</em> - No longer constrained by 90s console hardware, your
        experience will now be as silky smooth as your modern GPU and monitor can handle!</li>
      <li><em>Enhancements</em> - Make your own fun! With a plethora of enhancements and cheats
        available, you're guaranteed to find a new way to play!</li>
      <li><em>Randomizer</em> - Shuffle what rewards you get from things like chests, skulltulas,
        and more with the built-in randomizer! Endless replayability! No patching required!</li>
    </ul>
    <p>2Ship does not include any copyrighted assets. You are required to provide a
      supported copy of the game.</p>
  </description>
